Any ideas as to why meta descriptions aren't being passed from the content editor, back to the template? I have all suggested markup in my header files, i.e. 		

&lt;!-- ==============================================
		Title and Meta Tags
		=============================================== --&gt;
		&lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;
        &lt;title&gt;{{ content.html_title }}&lt;/title&gt;
        {{ standard_header_includes }}

		&lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"&gt;
		&lt;meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"&gt;
